  "detailed_description": "<h1>CHAOS ON WHEELS - DELUXE EDITION</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1623120/extras/72cac5585bb4d8c18eb60472d8aba87d.avif?t=1760358424\" width=614 height=346 /></span>Deluxe Edition includes:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Chaos on Wheels - Base Game</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Start your Chaos Career with Deluxe deadly machine: Furious Phoenix or Mad Royal</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get access to additional cars: Furious Phoenix - Mad Royal - Bobble - Torch</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get an additional 35% Cash Bonus</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get an additional 15% Experience Bonus</p></li></ul></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><strong>Chaos on Wheels</strong>: Casual singleplayer destruction car combat experience. Customize your cars, equip armor, buy weapons, unlock new gadgets, upgrade ammo, and fight other cars in a battle of total mayhem. Choose your driver and take the wheel of a heavily armored car. Drive yourself to victory by destroying any enemy that stands in your way. Avoid projectiles, traps, and hazards and bring chaos to anyone who opposes you. Complete achievements, upgrade cars, and make even more chaos. <br><br><strong>Key Features:</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1623120/extras/ba3824e275eb566f583cf3e8374c25e8.webp?t=1760358424\" width=620 height=38 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1623120/extras/2a99d503f4618bbb3cb27e2e1d4ac6a2.poster.avif?t=1760358424\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1623120/extras/2a99d503f4618bbb3cb27e2e1d4ac6a2.webm?t=1760358424\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1623120/extras/2a99d503f4618bbb3cb27e2e1d4ac6a2.mp4?t=1760358424\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Fast-paced action with tons of bullets, rockets, and missiles. Play with your friends and family on splitscreen; destroy them all, and leave nothing but chaos. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1623120/extras/92a0f03fa17a4a64dc85b25e0f19d125.webp?t=1760358424\" width=620 height=38 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1623120/extras/771acaad797924124aa50be4f1ec9968.poster.avif?t=1760358424\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1623120/extras/771acaad797924124aa50be4f1ec9968.webm?t=1760358424\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1623120/extras/771acaad797924124aa50be4f1ec9968.mp4?t=1760358424\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Begin your Chaos Career and manage a special garage where you can upgrade weapons, ammo, and armor. Equip new gadgets, add wraps, throw in some colors, and make your dream ride. Fill in all 5 slots with your deadly custom machines. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1623120/extras/748ad3c688c2babfd58c51e608cdcee4.webp?t=1760358424\" width=620 height=38 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1623120/extras/c0fbad1f3b605bdc57735b3bacc4cd06.poster.avif?t=1760358424\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1623120/extras/c0fbad1f3b605bdc57735b3bacc4cd06.webm?t=1760358424\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1623120/extras/c0fbad1f3b605bdc57735b3bacc4cd06.mp4?t=1760358424\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Pick your driver, buckle up, and unleash the power of your high-performance machine. Drive, drift, jump, and perform stunts to your heart's content.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1623120/extras/50bf86acec9a25ba40daa586f7593cd1.webp?t=1760358424\" width=620 height=38 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1623120/extras/451def985953d571377b6ce7007a410b.poster.avif?t=1760358424\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1623120/extras/451def985953d571377b6ce7007a410b.webm?t=1760358424\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1623120/extras/451def985953d571377b6ce7007a410b.mp4?t=1760358424\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Don't forget about Turrets and Hazards. They are there to stop you! Destroy them first to unlock new cars, weapons, armor, or gadgets, and leave Helios and his turret army in ashes in a unique 10-chapter campaign.",
  "about_the_game": "<strong>Chaos on Wheels</strong>: Casual singleplayer destruction car combat experience. Customize your cars, equip armor, buy weapons, unlock new gadgets, upgrade ammo, and fight other cars in a battle of total mayhem. Choose your driver and take the wheel of a heavily armored car. Drive yourself to victory by destroying any enemy that stands in your way. Avoid projectiles, traps, and hazards and bring chaos to anyone who opposes you. Complete achievements, upgrade cars, and make even more chaos. <br><br><strong>Key Features:</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1623120/extras/ba3824e275eb566f583cf3e8374c25e8.webp?t=1760358424\" width=620 height=38 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1623120/extras/2a99d503f4618bbb3cb27e2e1d4ac6a2.poster.avif?t=1760358424\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1623120/extras/2a99d503f4618bbb3cb27e2e1d4ac6a2.webm?t=1760358424\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1623120/extras/2a99d503f4618bbb3cb27e2e1d4ac6a2.mp4?t=1760358424\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Fast-paced action with tons of bullets, rockets, and missiles. Play with your friends and family on splitscreen; destroy them all, and leave nothing but chaos. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1623120/extras/92a0f03fa17a4a64dc85b25e0f19d125.webp?t=1760358424\" width=620 height=38 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1623120/extras/771acaad797924124aa50be